text: House at 209-211 S. Ninth Street was a historic home located at Terre Haute, Vigo County, Indiana. It was built about 1880, and was a one-story, Late Victorian rectangular frame duplex cottage. It featured an elaborate Eastlake Movement style front porch with a shed roof. Note: This includes and It has been demolished. It was listed on the National Register of Historic Places in 1983, and was delisted in 2019. Site of the house at 209-211 S.
